commit.message:
Some gcdmaster fixes

- fix size of CDTEXT dialog
- use Gtk::Grid instead of Gtk::Table
- allow gcdmaster to open a toc file from command line
- use UTF-8 when importing CDTEXT
mp3 conversion bug fix with libao
ChangeLog update for 1.2.5. Add encoding test toc
fix the --swap argument so it works with the generic-mmc-raw driver as expected
CdTextItem encoding and mem mgmt reorg
C++11 Reorg, added params to print() function
Added Toc support for character encoding
toc2mp3 support for character encoding in filenames and id3v2 tags
